latestIgtvVideos.title: A Love Letter To The City
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
-
-
In making of your bright future do not forget to look back at your bright memories. You are nothing without your memory lane. We always roam around and meet new environment whether it is in form of human or nature, but it will leave with finch of memory. For that travel is best part to live million lives. 
Here is a beautiful visuals of our small little journeys with those all people who accompanied us whether it was small auto rickshaw drive, road trip, andheri to church gate train or running with the clouds. Sometimes alone sometimes with bunch of idiots and also with someone with whom we never filmed but they were always in heart. 
@harshjanii @swatscapture @hirendixit1 @rjharsh04 @whyshestyled @harvijay_j @sid8mistry @iyerhariharan @caffeinated.shimmer ❤️
-
